<class name="General_Resource" inherits="Node" version="4.0">
    <brief_description>
        Creates a generic object that holds a maximum 'resource' value and a current 'resource' value
    </brief_description>
    <description>
        Intended to be used for player resource values such as health, mana, energy, etc. Minimum value is 0. 'Maximum' and 'Current' value initialize as 0 but can be updated. Logic in place to prevent 'Current' from exceeding 'Maximum'. 'Maximum' and 'Current' cannot go below 0.
    </description>

